name: WorkoutExcuseMaker
0:
”Alexa. Open Workout Excuse Maker”
”Alexa. Open Workout Excuse Maker and give me an excuse”
”Alexa. Open Workout Excuse Maker and make up an excuse”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: workout excuse maker
des:
We have all skipped workouts before and felt guilty about it. Use this Alexa Skill to give yourself some peace of mind. Know that missing the workout was really beyond your control and goof off guilt-free!

This skill will work on the amazon echo product family and displays Workout Excuse Maker cards in the Alexa app as you interact with it.

Say "Alexa. Open Workout Excuse Maker" or "Alexa. Open Workout Excuse Maker and give me one" to start missing your workout today!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
